column21: Dr Shylesh Shetty is amongst the pioneers of microscope centered endodontics in the country. Dr. Shylesh Shetty completed his BDS in the year 1999 and went on to do his masters in endodontics. Soon after the completion of his masters in the year 2004, Dr. Shetty held faculty positions at the Rajiv Gandhi University of Health Sciences. Between the years 2004 - 09 Dr. Shetty was a consultant Endodontist at many of central and east Bangalore's leading dental practices. Realizing that the highest standard of endodontic care required was not deliverable as a consultant in a "General Dentistry" set-ups, Dr.Shylesh  Shetty set up the "Root Canal center"- in the year 2008- a unique specialty endodontic practice, the cornerstone of the practice being the surgical microscope - a tool that sets the standard of excellence. Root canal treatment is performed completely under the operating microscope which allows complete visualization of the main and accessory root canal system and requires a high degree of skill and training, the vision of successful treatment outcome being based on the use of cutting edge technology, equipment, knowledge, and skill - the unique combination that results in very high long-term success. Keen on raising the bar of endodontic standards in India, Dr. Shylesh Shetty is passionately involved in training endodontists on the latest advances in endodontic techniques and concepts through lectures and hands-on training at his " Micro- endodontic" training facility in Bangalore. “Excellence Dental”- was set up by Dr Shetty in June 2016, as an extension of the “Root canal centre” with the intent of providing the highest global standards of care across dental specialties under one roof. To this end, Dr. Shetty has put together a team of carefully selected set of practitioners and specialists chosen for their knowledge, experience and skill in their respective fields. This closely curated team brings together a new generation of dental craftsmanship.

column21: COVID PROTOCOL (MAY 2020) Dr Ganesh Shetty and his staff follow the most stringent protocol of disinfection and sanitization to ensure complete safety of their patients. A few of the extra precautions and machinery used to achieve this are mentioned below-   1)Class B autoclave(EURONDA) for sterilizing instruments 2)U.V Sterilizers for additional sterilization 3)Continuous disinfection of all surfaces in the operatory and waiting area 4)Fogging machine to sanitize all upholstery and dental chairs 5)Cold sterilization of dental instruments  6)Ensuring that patients adhere to strict appointment times to minimize waiting or crowding in the reception area 7)Hand sanitizers and povidone-iodine microbicidal rinse given to all patients 8)Extra-oral suction used to minimize aerosol generation   Dr. Ganesh Shetty practices at Dental and Orthodontic Clinic. Worked in M S Ramaiah Dental College in the Department of Oral Pathology. Currently starting work in the second branch of Dental and Orthodontic Clinic. With more than 14  years of experience in providing dental service to hundreds of customers, Dr. Ganesh Shetty is one of the premier dentists in Bangalore.

column21: Dr. Yamini brings in rich 10 years of experience in general dentistry and specialized in Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery. She graduated MDS from VKIDS, KLE University, Belagavi and BDS from YMTDC, Navi Mumbai. She is also a University certified Implantologist and participated in many national and international workshops on Dental Implants and Full Mouth Rehabilitation of patients with Parafunction and Temporomandibular Disorders. She has many awards and accomplishments to her name, presented scientific papers in many national and international conferences. Her deep interest in surgeries motivated her to further pursue research in streams such as Plastic surgery, Neurosurgery, Head & Neck Oncosurgery, Cleft & Craniofacial surgery. Her expertise in Dental Implants, Full Mouth Rehabilitation, Dentoalveolar Surgery, Benign Pathology, Soft & Hard tissue trauma and Secondary deformities of Oral & Maxillofacial region, Neuralgias, TMJ Disorders/Ankylosis and Dentofacial deformities helped deliver many happy smiles.

column21: Dr. Harshita Reddy S specializes in the field of ‘Paediatric And Preventive Dentistry’. She pursued her postgraduate studies from the reputed A B Shetty Memorial Institute of Dental Sciences, Mangalore  she honed her skills and developed a deep understanding of specialized dental care for children . She has an experience of over 3 years in handling various pediatric dental issues. She specialises in providing comprehensive dental therapies like pulpectomy, full coverage crowns , aesthetic restorations ,habit-breaking appliances , interceptive orthodontics etc .  Dr. Harshita’s inquisitiveness in the field helps her stay up to date by acquiring knowledge on the latest preventive therapies which include minimal invasive dentistry, silver diamine fluoride and remineralising agents to name a few. Her deep love for children inspired her to continue exploring and specialising in the treatment of children with special healthcare needs.

column21: Dr. Prerana Choudary is a highly skilled dentist specializing in Conservative Dentistry and Endodontics, with a robust academic background and extensive professional experience. After completing her BDS from The Oxford Dental College and Hospital, Bangalore, she pursued advanced training, including a Master Clinician Program in Integrated Clinical Endodontics from the American Association of Endodontists (AAE). Dr. Prearana Choudary's dedication to continuous learning is evident through her MDS from the Bangalore Institute of Dental Sciences and Hospital, RGUHS, where she focused on Conservative Dentistry and Endodontics. With expertise in advanced Rotary Endodontics, Cosmetic Dentistry, Post Endodontic Restorations, Vital Pulp Therapies, Endodontic Therapies under Magnification & other dental  specialized procedures, Dr. Choudary is committed to providing comprehensive and personalized dental care. Her proficiency in restoring fractured teeth, performing vital pulp therapies, and utilizing advanced endodontic techniques reflects her unwavering commitment to excellence in dentistry, ensuring optimal oral health and aesthetic satisfaction for her patients.
